haReport:
This mission was flown by:
Kmdr Patrik Schorner
Ltn Detlef Schwarzer
Ltn Joachim Lechner
Fw Ingemar Beckermann

 The mission was flown from Balatre,E Roye aerodrome.

Successes include the following: 
On 14/10/1916 near Prosnes.
A F.E.2b of Esc 111 was brought down by Wenzel Scheiner of Jasta 16b.
S/Lt Florentin Mayaud was killed in action.
S/Lt Jean-Marie Dages was killed in action.
Wenzel Scheiner was  flying a Albatros D.II.

On 14/10/1916 near City(f) Balatre.
A Nieuport 17.C1 GBR of No 1 Squadron RFC was brought down by Patrik Schorner of Jasta 16b.
Carney Younger was killed in action.
Patrik Schorner was  flying a Albatros D.II.

On 14/10/1916 near City(f) Balatre.
A Nieuport 17.C1 GBR of No 1 Squadron RFC was brought down by Patrik Schorner of Jasta 16b.
Hale Bardolf was killed in action.
Patrik Schorner was  flying a Albatros D.II.

On 14/10/1916 near City(f) Balatre.
A Nieuport 17.C1 GBR of No 1 Squadron RFC was brought down by Joachim Lechner of Jasta 16b.
Benjamin Wilkins was killed in action.
Joachim Lechner was  flying a Albatros D.II.

On 14/10/1916 near Moncel-sur-Seille.
A F.E.2b of Esc 29 was brought down by Rudiger Bretschneider of Jasta 16b.
Sergt Casimir Laborie was killed in action.
Lt Adolphe de Vauplane was killed in action.
Rudiger Bretschneider was  flying a Albatros D.II.

On 14/10/1916 near Camp.
A F.E.2b of No 23 Squadron RFC was brought down by Bernd Treich of Jasta 16b.
Lt Homer Leverer was killed in action.
Cpt Archer Burress was killed in action.
Bernd Treich was  flying a Albatros D.II.
